transform = Transform3D(30, 0, 0, 0, 10, 0, 0, 0, 20, 37, 5, 38)
message = "The Wolf will patrol the major points of interest of the map, becoming more and more alert with every spot they reach.

If it can hear you, it will look for your light.
If it sees your light, it will start to give chase.

The wolf's maximum speed is faster than yours.
You can slow it down by attacking it with your torch, but the timing is difficult.

If you are caught, you can save yourself by attacking when you see a red flash.
Failing this will result in your death."
duration = 30.0
one_shot = true

